   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [

   "source": [
    "filename='saved_model.sav'\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    with open(filename,'wb') as file:\n",
    "        pickle.dump(model,file)\n",
